title: UFO task force eyed as lawmaker warns of strange objects in skies and waters defying known technology
description: Vermont UFO task force proposed by Rep. Troy Headrick would investigate unidentified anomalous phenomena reports and assess airspace safety risks in coordination with federal partners.

title: Secret Danish UFO Contactees Reveal Aliens Have Spoken to Europe for Centuries
description: Little-known Danish contactees claim extraterrestrials have been speaking to Europe for centuries, from a mysterious 1600 sighting to modern links with Ashtar Command.

title: UFO Whistleblowers Claim Earth Is A Cosmic Farm Where Aliens Harvest Human Misery
description: UFO whistleblowers claim Earth is a cosmic farm where higher beings harvest human emotional energy, a concept rooted in Robert Monroe's 1985 book and later reshaped by David Icke.

title: Rendlesham UFO Allegedly Implanted A Chilling Doomsday Warning In A Soldier's Brain
description: A renewed wave of interest in the Rendlesham Forest case centres on claims that a UFO implanted a chilling binary warning into a soldier's mind.

title: UAP Whistleblower Gerb Says Battelle Job Carousel Shields Alien Secrets From Americans
description: UAP whistleblower 'Gerb' accuses a Battelle-linked job carousel of shielding UFO secrets, suppressing truth or manipulating disclosure.
